---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About kira w.">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-7">

        <h1 style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">About</h1>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.875rem;margin-bottom:3rem;">the person behind the blog</p>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Hello world! I'm Kira. I started this blog because I think it's cool that a little corner 
            of the infinitely expanding internet is mine. I love doing a lot of things: I play piano, violin, 
            occassionally do math, computer science (I make silly little apps). Maybe I'm mediocre at a lot of them,
            but I really love learning and sharing my ideas :)
          </p>
          <p>
            Right now I'm still trying to figure things out. I'm not really sure what I enjoy, or what I want to do when
            I'm older, but I'm trying to explore as many things as I can. I'm currently trying to learn Rust, regression, and physics through various textbooks or online sources.
            I have so many exams but I'm doing my best to stay curious. 
          </p>
          <p>
            This blog is a little record of things I've worked through or thought about. Some of it are fragments of undeveloped
            thought (so do not expect anything of substance). I'm currently working on getting a comment section (harder than you may think),
            so look out for that soon!
          </p>

          <h2>socials!</h2>
          <p>
            <a href="mailto:kikisadventures37@gmail.com">kikisadventures37@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
